         <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en">
            <p>In this tomb lies the body of Irasius, of good memory. He lived [in peace] for more or less 17 years; he left this world on day fourteen of month September. 
               May Christ who has called you receive you; may angels escort you into the bosom of Abraham.</p>
